ATTRIBUTION STATEMENT

This software is based on anyclaude, originally developed by Coder Technologies Inc.
The original project provided the core proxy architecture for translating between
the Anthropic Messages API and OpenAI Chat Completions format.

Significant enhancements in this fork include:
- vLLM-MLX auto-launch support with prompt caching
- OpenRouter integration for cloud model access
- Comprehensive automated test suite (1,400+ tests)
- Enhanced tool calling reliability
- Trace logging system for prompt analysis
- Multi-mode architecture (vllm-mlx, lmstudio, openrouter, claude)

